          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The target system consists of 4 single cylinders",
                "filled with neon at normal pressure. They were arranged",
                "and adjusted similar to a stacked foil system.",
                "The individual targets consist of a silver plated",
                "brass cylinders of 20 mm inner diameter and 25 mm",
                "length, sealed by 20 mm aluminium windows. Silver",
                "coating was used to trap the fluorine as water-soluble",
                "AgF on the wall surface.",
                "In addition, the inner surface was coated with a thin",
                "layer of NaF by evaporating an aqueous NaF solution.",
                "Each target is equipped with two valves for rinsing",
                "the 18-F from the wall after irradiation."
              ]
            }
          ],
